data.description: Motivated Seller! Fresh Paint, Welcome to this inviting open floor plan in the heart of Spring Hill, where comfort meets convenience. This home offers an open split floor plan with vaulted ceilings that adds dimension to this three bedroom, two bath, two car garage home on an oversized lot. Concerned about the insurance issues regarding roofs in Florida? No need to worry, this roof was replaced in 2020, making it less than 4 years old-with a long lifespan ahead! In additional to the newer roof, one of the stand out features is the fenced in-oversized (1/3 acre) lot.  This fenced in backyard is a perfect haven for dog lovers or gardening enthusiasts, or anyone who enjoys the serene outside scenery. There is plenty of room to add a pool if you choose to. Another key advantage to this property: No HOA Community Fees/Rules or Community District Development Fees.  This property is definitely worth your consideration, whether you're seeking a primary residence or an investment opportunity.  Act quickly, schedule your viewing today!  While the home may need some upgrading and your personal touch, the price is reflective of that. Hernando is a growing county yet still within an hour drive to local Amusement Parks, Beaches such as: Clearwater, Honeymoon Island, Dunedin Causeway, Tarpon Springs. Give me a call today and schedule your viewing, allow me to be part of creating a lifestyle you won't need a vacation from.
